      "writtenOn": "2020-08-28T19:16:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Now that SkParagraphImpl constructors are taking std::unique_ptr\u003cSkUnicode\u003e can we just assert in the constructors that it\u0027s non-nullptr? That\u0027s what we really want, which not to be able to create a ParagraphImpl without a working SkUnicode.",
