        "id": 5140
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-28T20:56:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I suppose we could have our own UTF encoding converter but the reality is that everyone already has one and it would be nice to just use an existing one if we can.\n\nSkUnicode basically has to be provided to Paragraph by a user at some point. If Paragraph just says \u0027I\u0027m always just going to use the ICU one\u0027 then it might as well just use ICU directly and not go through any of this.",
      "parentUuid": "28ea21a5_21ed3cd3",
